tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE dish_popularity (
    dish_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    dish_name VARCHAR(50),
    cuisine_id INT,
    sales_count INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (cuisine_id) REFERENCES cuisine_sales(cuisine_id)
);
CREATE TABLE cuisine (id INT PRIMARY KEY, cuisine_name VARCHAR(255), cuisine_type VARCHAR(255))
CREATE TABLE dish (id INT PRIMARY KEY, dish_name VARCHAR(255), cuisine_id INT, price DECIMAL(10,2))
CREATE TABLE sales (id INT PRIMARY KEY, dish_id INT, quantity INT, sale_date DATE))
CREATE TABLE popular_dish (id INT PRIMARY KEY, dish_id INT, popularity_rank INT)
CREATE TABLE Cuisine (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL, region VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL, description TEXT)
CREATE TABLE Dish (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL, cuisine_id INT NOT NULL, price DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL, rating FLOAT NOT NULL)
CREATE TABLE Order (id INT PRIMARY KEY, dish_id INT NOT NULL, quantity INT NOT NULL, order_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL)
CREATE TABLE Customer (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL, email VARCHAR(255) UNIQUE)
CREATE TABLE Feedback (id INT PRIMARY KEY, order_id INT NOT NULL, rating FLOAT NOT NULL, comment TEXT)
